title: 33 Cool Decor Items That’ll Blast My New Apartment With Some Personality
description: You won't believe how cool these pieces are.
excerpt: Shop these cool home decor pieces to add a bit of fun and personality into your home.
text: Whether you’ve just moved into a new place or you’ve been in the same living situation for many years, sometimes adding some fresh pieces to your space breathes new life into your home and gives you a little extra dose of happy chemicals to fuel your everyday. I recently moved into a studio apartment, and I’ve been scouring the internet retail scene for some pieces and hacks for injecting a little bit more personality into my apartment. Since I know how overwhelming the online shopping world can be, I’ve decided to include some of it. My favorite finds from my home decor internet sleuthing sessions.From unique lamps to the prettiest side tables, there are so many gorgeous finds that I’ve hand-picked ahead for your shopping pleasure. You can expect top-tier picks from Wayfair, Urban Outfitters, Lulu and Georgia, Zara, Amazon and so much more. Keep scrolling to uncover your next favorite home decor find today.
